(define/contract (min-processing-time processorTime tasks)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)
  
  (let* ([n (length processorTime)]
         [sorted-tasks (sort tasks >)]
         [cores-per-processor (* n 4)]
         [allocated-tasks (make-vector n 0)]
         [processor-availability (apply vector processorTime)])
    
    (for ([task sorted-tasks])
      (let ([min-index (let loop ([i 0] [min-i 0] [min-val (vector-ref processor-availability 0)])
                         (if (< i n)
                             (let ([current-val (vector-ref processor-availability i)])
                               (if (< current-val min-val)
                                   (loop (+ i 1) i current-val)
                                   (loop (+ i 1) min-i min-val)))
                             min-i))])
        (vector-set! processor-availability min-index (+ task (vector-ref processor-availability min-index)))
        (vector-set! allocated-tasks min-index (+ 1 (vector-ref allocated-tasks min-index)))))
    
    (let ([completion-times (for/list ([i (in-range n)])
                               (vector-ref processor-availability i))])
      (apply max completion-times))))
